list.name: Annotation
list.query: select text,tags,title from "$retention"."events" where application =~ /$app/ AND $timeFilter

targets.query: SELECT last("startedT") FROM "jmeter" WHERE "application" =~ /$app$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($granularity) fill(null)
SELECT "hit" FROM "jmeter" WHERE "application" =~ /$app$/ AND "statut" = 'all' AND $timeFilter
SELECT mean("countError")  / 5 FROM "jmeter" WHERE "application" =~ /$app$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($granularity) fill(0)
SELECT mean("value") FROM "jmeter.all.a.max" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT last("min") FROM "$retention"."jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$app$/ AND "statut" = 'all') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($granularity)
SELECT last("avg") FROM "$retention"."jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$app$/ AND "statut" = 'all') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval)
SELECT sum("count")  / 30 FROM "$retention"."jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$app$/ AND "transaction" <> 'all' AND "statut" = 'all') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval), "transaction"
SELECT last("hit")  / 5 FROM "$retention"."jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$app$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($granularity) fill(null)
SELECT sum("hit")  / 30 FROM "$retention"."jmeter" WHERE "application" = '$app' AND "transaction" = 'all' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(30)
SELECT mean("hit")/30 FROM "$retention"."jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$app$/ AND "statut" = 'all') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($granularity)
SELECT last("hit")  / 30 FROM "$retention"."jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$app$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($granularity) fill(null)
SELECT sum("countError")  / sum("count") FROM "$retention"."jmeter" WHERE "application" =~ /$app$/ AND "transaction" = 'all' AND $timeFilter
SELECT sum("min")  / 30 FROM "$retention"."jmeter" WHERE "application" = '$app' AND "transaction" = 'all' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(30)
SELECT last("max") FROM "$retention"."jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$app$/ AND "statut" = 'all') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($granularity)  fill(null)
SELECT last("max") FROM "jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /^$app$/ AND "statut" = 'ok') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT last("avg") FROM "$retention"."jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$app$/ AND "statut" = 'all') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval)
SELECT sum("count")  / 30 FROM "$retention"."jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$app$/ AND "transaction" <> 'all' AND "statut" = 'all') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(30s), "transaction"
SELECT mean("avg") FROM "$retention"."jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$app$/ AND "statut" = 'all') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($granularity), "transaction"
SELECT sum("count")  / 30 FROM "$retention"."jmeter" WHERE ("application" =~ /$app$/ AND "transaction" <> 'all' AND "statut" = 'all') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($granularity), "transaction"
SELECT last("count")  / 30 FROM "$retention"."jmeter" WHERE "application" =~ /$app$/ AND "statut" = 'ko' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(30s), "transaction" fill(null)
SELECT sum("count")  / 5 FROM "jmeter" WHERE "application" =~ /$app$/ AND "statut" = 'ko' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($granularity), "responseCode" fill(null)

list.name: app
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "jmeter" WITH KEY = "application"
list.tagsQuery: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "events" WITH KEY = "tags"

list.name: transaction
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "jmeter" WITH KEY IN ("transaction","application") where application =~ /$app/ and transaction  !~ /all/
